                <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
                    <li><p class="text-sm font-bold">Bachelors of Science in Anthropology</p>
                        <p class="text-xs">Troy University c/o 2016</p>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary font-neuebit leading-[2rem] pt-4">Experience</h2>
            <p>A brief overview of my professional journey.</p>
