                    <p class="text-xs">Jul 2022 - Sep 2023 · 1 yr 3 mos</p>
                </li>
                <li><p class="text-sm font-bold">Self-Employed</p>
                    <p class="text-xs">Digital Swan - Digital Marketing Agency</p>
                    <p class="text-xs">Jul 2020 - Jun 2022 · 2 yrs</p>
                </li>
                <li><p class="text-sm font-bold">Creative Director & Lead Web Developer</p>
                    <p class="text-xs">Digital Marketing Agency</p>
                    <p class="text-xs">Jul 2017 - Jul 2020 · 3 yrs 1 mos</p>
                </li>
            </ul>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary font-neuebit leading-[2rem] pt-4">Skills</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-sm">
                <li><span class="font-bold">Languages:</span> HTML, CSS, Javascript, Typescript, PHP
                </li>
                <li><span class="font-bold">Frameworks:</span> React, Astro, Wordpress
