                <li><span class="font-bold">Email Platforms:</span> ActiveCampaign, Mailchimp, Flodesk, ConvertKit</li>
                <li><span class="font-bold">Other:</span> APIs, Google Analytics, Looker Studio, Stripe
                </li>
            </ul>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary font-neuebit leading-[2rem] pt-4">Projects</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
                <li><p class="text-sm font-bold">The Counter</p>
                    <p class="text-xs">Client task management app for Pixel brew.</p>
                    <p class="text-xs"><span class="font-bold">Stack:</span> React, Express, MongoDB, Typescript, Tailwind, DaisyUI, Tanstack Router & Query, Websockets</p>
                </li>
                <li><p class="text-sm font-bold">Pixel Brew Website</p>
                    <p class="text-xs">Website for Pixel Brew</p>
                    <p class="text-xs"><span class="font-bold">Stack:</span> Astro, Tailwind, DaisyUI, Vite</p>
                </li>
                <li><p class="text-sm font-bold">StarNotes</p>
                    <p class="text-xs">A note taking app that stores the astrological data for the moment.</p>
